What is the time complexity of the following code snippet? 
for (int i = 0; i < n; i = i + c) { 
  // O(1) operations 
}

What is the time complexity of the following code snippet? 
for (int i = n; i > 1; i = i / c) { 
  // O(1) operations 
}

What is the time complexity of this nested loop structure? 
for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) { 
  for (int j = 1; j < n; j = j * 2) { 
    // O(1) operations 
  } 
}

What is the time complexity of the following code where the inner loop depends on the outer loop's variable? 
for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) { 
  for (int j = 1; j <= i; j++) { 
    // O(1) operations 
  } 
}

What is the time complexity of the following code? 
for (int i = 1; i <= N; i++) { 
  for (int j = 1; j <= N; j += i) { 
    // O(1) operations 
  } 
}

What is the time complexity of two independent sequential loops executed one after the other? 
for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) { } 
for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) { }

